title._content: One Portion of the Former Home of Aviatrix Amelia Earhart Who Disappeared on a Round the World Flight in the Late 1930's...06/1974

description._content: Original Caption: One Portion of the Former Home of Aviatrix Amelia Earhart Who Disappeared on a Round the World Flight in the Late 1930's. The Atchison, Kansas, House Is a Beautiful Example of Neo-Classical Wooden Victorian Architecture Built on a High Bluff Overlooking the Missouri River.
